      "Converting YouTube videos to MP3 format is one of the most popular uses of video downloading tools. Whether you want to save a music performance, extract audio from a lecture, keep a podcast episode for offline listening, or create a workout playlist from your favorite tracks, converting to MP3 gives you a lightweight audio file that works on any device.",
      "## Why Convert to MP3?",
      "Video files contain both visual and audio data, making them significantly larger than audio-only files. A 4-minute music video at 1080p might be 80-120 MB, while the same audio extracted as an MP3 is only about 4-6 MB. That's a 95% reduction in file size while keeping the content you actually want to listen to.",
