      "Many MP3 players and music apps can read ID3 tags — metadata embedded in the MP3 file that includes the song title, artist, album, and genre. You can edit these tags using free tools like MP3Tag (Windows) or Kid3 (Mac/Linux) to make your library searchable and organized.",
      "## Legal and Ethical Considerations",
