    slug: "video-resolution-explained",
    title: "Video Resolution Explained: 360p to 8K — What's the Difference?",
    excerpt: "Understand video resolutions, when each quality level matters, and how to choose the right one for your needs.",
    category: "Guide",
    readTime: "8 min read",
